{"tid":1379163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位和理非如果連罷工咁低成本既抗爭都唔做 我地仲點對得住前線既年青人","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T05:18:37.000Z","uid":41411,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d81954ccec56b7498bd0def11f4574bc01f1d6","tid":1379163,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:51:58.000Z","msg":"無論係私人市場定公務員 都希望你地參與8月5號全港大罷工 唔會因為一日罷工就比人炒架！<br />\n<br />\n明白大家本身有唔同既角色 有唔同既責任 所以唔可以企上前線<br />\n但當你地係屋企睇住Live...見到班年青人為左香港 為左公義 不惜冒上生命危險同牢獄之災...去同敵人對抗到最後<br />\n見到佢地比人拉 會唔會覺得好內疚？會唔會問自己點解唔敢同佢地企係同一陣線...點解拋棄左佢地...<br />\n<br />\n係依一刻，當我地仲未有心理準備加入勇武派既一分子<br />\n我地可以做到而又有影響力既就只有罷工！罷市！罷課！<br />\n如果我地連咁低成本既抗爭都做唔到，我地仲對唔對得住企係前線為我地流血流淚既年青人？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下大家，我地香港人要團結喇！今次唔可以認輸呀！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wfqCsKr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwfqCsKr.png&h=561e2719&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eq2k9XN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEq2k9XN.png&h=60c7a3ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d721febb74a081d5cfb67a7cb3f9d8065e4b531","tid":1379163,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:55:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f77a7c739a6a74517d855aaa7f25c98985ff06bd","tid":1379163,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c660e1ea7bb16016620d33fe86be7de96f8f62","tid":1379163,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca44b687fd27fd33f8ac8af6325b0fee160e6ed","tid":1379163,"uid":137048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:55:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7687557f080cb5a161775bc3d